34:28.785 --> 34:46.122
trees are going to die, and there's not going to be 
anything there to replace it and I think it would be

34:47.063 --> 34:58.813
the most critical error that we could make if we got 
to the point where we actually destroy the

34:47.063 --> 34:58.813
character of our living forest that we have today. 
